fields.name: Dungeons And Dragons Starter kit
fields.description: The Dungeons & Dragons Starter Set is your gateway to action-packed stories of the imagination. This box contains the essential rules of the game plus everything you need to play heroic characters on perilous adventures in worlds of fantasy.

fields.name: Zoo Vadis
fields.description: Zoo Vadis is a game of strategy and skill. Players must build their own zoo and attract as many visitors as possible. The player with the most visitors at the end of the game wins.

fields.name: Witchcraft
fields.description: Witchcraft is a game of strategy and skill. Players must build their own coven and cast spells to defeat their opponents. The player with the most powerful coven at the end of the game wins.
